reviewText: Super happy I found this. Great price too
Don't know how the movies were, when i looked at the product detail it did not say anything about them being for region 2 and didn't see anything about the disk being shipped from Europe.

I liked all for films; but, I liked the crocodile films the best. I have a lot of shark films already and so they were only average for my interests. I have several Alligator films and always liked that creature a lot. Crocodiles remind me more than the others of the days of the dinosaurs and there feriousity. The crocodile films were great for me.
